---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Codex Guide">
  <section class="card">
    <div class="eyebrow">Tool Guide</div>
    <h1>Codex</h1>
    <p>Codex is the primary happy-path CLI for the first public beta.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use <code>codex exec --full-auto</code> for the beta path.</li>
      <li>Add <code>--skip-git-repo-check</code> when the working directory is not a git repo.</li>
      <li>Current beta does not yet support per-chat Codex session-id resume.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
